# Project Structure

This is a TypeScript project for learning JavaScript with OpenAI API integration.

## Main Entry Points
- [index.ts](mdc:index.ts) - Main application entry point with OpenAI API integration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project configuration and scripts

## Core Utilities
- [utils/env.ts](mdc:utils/env.ts) - Environment configuration with Zod validation

## Configuration Files
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration with strict settings
- [biome.json](mdc:biome.json) - Linting and formatting configuration
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project documentation

## Development Workflow
The project uses modern TypeScript with ES modules, strict type checking, and Biome for code quality.
